title: Keds Women's Kickback Sneaker
description: A slip-on that looks like a lace-up—the Kickback sneaker takes easygoing to a whole new level. For starters, it has an already broken-in feel straight out of the box thanks to relaxed uppers, super soft jersey lining, and cushiony footbeds. Add to that the clever slip-on-in-disguise design with its stretch gore on the inside and pull tabs for easy on-and-offs and they go straight to the top of the sneakers-to-live-in category.
